Kami akan segera kembali.
- Tidak, Rudra.

00:18:59.168 --> 00:19:02.328
Mari kita temukan bersama.  Datang.

00:19:02.368 --> 00:19:03.408
Pergilah sayang.

00:19:08.968 --> 00:19:10.128
Datang.

00:19:11.368 --> 00:19:12.168
Rudra.

00:19:13.488 --> 00:19:15.088
